abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Virginia Tech women's basketball team defeats Tennessee, 57-43; other women's and men's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Vanessa Panousis scored 21 points and shot 5 of 8 from 3-point range as Virginia Tech continued its fast start with a 57-43 upset of No. 8 Tennessee on Sunday.

headline.main: Tennessee Women Are Upset, With Fewest Points Since ’74
